1
00:00:00,210 --> 00:00:02,110
The name that promised we'd be one.

2
00:00:04,040 --> 00:00:05,040
- Wanna One. - Wanna One.

3
00:00:07,010 --> 00:00:10,320
All that was built up around that name was years of curiosity.

4
00:00:11,980 --> 00:00:13,920
- The answer was Wannable. - Wannable.

5
00:00:17,020 --> 00:00:19,820
Our once-frozen time is flowing again.

6
00:00:20,730 --> 00:00:21,930
For the past seven years...

7
00:00:22,460 --> 00:00:23,730
We lived in our own world...

8
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:25,930
without each other.

9
00:00:26,900 --> 00:00:28,700
Despite that, we still remembered this.

10
00:00:29,700 --> 00:00:30,940
When Wannables come together,

11
00:00:31,570 --> 00:00:32,940
- so does Wanna One. - So does Wanna One.

12
00:00:34,410 --> 00:00:36,510
We have reunited again at the call of Wannables...

13
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:39,240
and gathered at the Wanna Base.

14
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:41,350
At the base, we laugh together.

15
00:00:42,310 --> 00:00:43,420
We eat together.

16
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:45,220
We go to sleep together.

17
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:47,950
Whatever it is, we must do it together.

18
00:00:48,820 --> 00:00:49,820
And...

19
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,890
- Wannables will join us too. - Wannables will join us too.

20
00:00:54,190 --> 00:00:56,260
Our confession after seven years.

21
00:00:58,430 --> 00:01:00,530
WANNA ONE GO: Back to Base.

22
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,540
It begins now.

23
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:27,529
- WANNA ONE GO... - WANNA ONE GO...

24
00:01:27,530 --> 00:01:29,129
- WANNA ONE GO... - WANNA ONE GO...

25
00:01:29,130 --> 00:01:30,499
- Will begin. - Will begin.

26
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:31,899
- Will begin. - Will begin.

27
00:01:31,900 --> 00:01:32,900
One, two, three.

28
00:01:34,300 --> 00:01:36,499
- WANNA ONE GO, let's go! - Let's go!

29
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:37,800
- Bye. - Bye.

30
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:39,469
- Park Ji Hoon! - Ji Hoon!

31
00:01:39,470 --> 00:01:41,109
- Thank you. - Congratulations.

32
00:01:41,110 --> 00:01:43,809
I'll try my best to show you good performances...

33
00:01:43,810 --> 00:01:45,940
as a member of Wanna One in 2026.

34
00:01:46,610 --> 00:01:47,680
I did

35
00:01:47,850 --> 00:01:50,109
(The day before the start of WANNA ONE GO)

36
00:01:50,110 --> 00:01:52,619
- Hello. - Hello.

37
00:01:52,620 --> 00:01:55,319
It's the day before the filming of WANNA ONE GO.

38
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:57,290
So I'm going to pack up for the shoot.

39
00:01:57,660 --> 00:01:59,760
The first item is my suitcase.

40
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,130
Wanna One is engraved on it.

41
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:05,800
This is...

42
00:02:05,801 --> 00:02:06,929
(I'll pack in my favourite suitcase.)

43
00:02:06,930 --> 00:02:07,930
the suitcase I prepared.

44
00:02:09,100 --> 00:02:11,139
(Wanna One Encyclopedia: Packing Styles for Their First Shoot)

45
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:13,200
(It may be unrelated to their actual personalities.)

46
00:02:13,940 --> 00:02:16,770
First of all, our fans loved seeing me in these last time.

47
00:02:17,110 --> 00:02:20,110
They really liked my teddy bear pyjamas.

48
00:02:20,380 --> 00:02:22,010
I'll pack my Bluetooth speaker just in case.

49
00:02:22,450 --> 00:02:24,150
I'll pack comfortable clothes.

50
00:02:24,620 --> 00:02:25,680
A variety of toiletries.

51
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:26,920
Cosmetics.

52
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:27,920
Razor.

53
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:28,920
Health supplements.

54
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:29,920
Chargers.

55
00:02:29,921 --> 00:02:31,120
(Min Hyun and Seong Wu pack only necessary items.)

56
00:02:31,390 --> 00:02:33,419
I like to bring all kinds of things with me.

57
00:02:33,420 --> 00:02:34,759
Vitamin supplements for my members.

58
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:36,859
I'm also packing face masks. I want to try with my members.

59
00:02:36,860 --> 00:02:39,829
Some of the members don't bring skincare products and face washes.

60
00:02:39,830 --> 00:02:41,929
So I packed a whole pouch of them.

61
00:02:41,930 --> 00:02:44,739
A member of our group used to borrow face washes from me.

62
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:48,869
And I remember this guy being a really good singer.

63
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:50,310
As for face washes and skincare products,

64
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:54,279
I'll gratefully borrow from my members.

65
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:56,510
(Brazen)

66
00:02:57,050 --> 00:02:59,049
I didn't have that much to pack. I packed underwear.

67
00:02:59,050 --> 00:03:01,019
(1 piece of underwear)

68
00:03:01,020 --> 00:03:02,020
That's it.

69
00:03:02,050 --> 00:03:05,220
I looked around to see what to pack, but I couldn't find anything.

70
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:07,929
Actually, it doesn't matter what I pack.

71
00:03:07,930 --> 00:03:11,260
At the thought of meeting our fans after all these years...

72
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:13,530
I'm quite excited for tomorrow.

73
00:03:13,930 --> 00:03:15,600
I have mixed feelings.

74
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:18,299
I'm a bit nervous.

75
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:19,569
(Clutching his heart)

76
00:03:19,570 --> 00:03:20,940
I'm also worried.

77
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:23,139
Actually, I'm getting the butterflies.

78
00:03:23,140 --> 00:03:25,510
Now that it's the day before the shoot, it feels surreal.

79
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:27,209
I feel a bit emotional.

80
00:03:27,210 --> 00:03:28,380
All right, Wannables.

81
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:30,550
See you soon! Bye.

82
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:33,950
(The day of the opening ceremony)

83
00:03:34,350 --> 00:03:35,350
(WANNA ONE GO: Back to Base, See you on Tuesday, April 28.)

84
00:03:35,351 --> 00:03:36,390
(DMC Cultural Park in Sangam)

85
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:38,319
(Despite the bad weather, Wannables filled the park...)

86
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,960
(waiting for the reunion after 7 years.)

87
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:42,929
(As countless Wannables gather hours before meeting Wanna One...)

88
00:03:42,930 --> 00:03:44,159
- Come here. - I love you.

89
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,260
(We didn't forget you for 7 years.)

90
00:03:45,730 --> 00:03:46,829
We've been waiting.

91
00:03:46,830 --> 00:03:47,830
(We're still here.)

92
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:50,339
(At the same time, in Wanna One's waiting room)

93
00:03:50,340 --> 00:03:52,739
(Daniel and Kuan Lin are waiting for their members.)

94
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:54,210
(Guys, get here already.)

95
00:03:55,370 --> 00:03:57,180
(Jin Young walks into the waiting room.)

96
00:03:57,510 --> 00:03:58,779
I'm the first one here.

97
00:03:58,780 --> 00:04:00,140
(Excited at the thought of meeting Wannables)

98
00:04:00,550 --> 00:04:02,609
(The members of Wanna One arrive one at a time with cheerful smiles.)

99
00:04:02,610 --> 00:04:03,920
Good morning.

100
00:04:04,580 --> 00:04:05,650
Hello.

101
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,849
It's been a long time.

102
00:04:07,850 --> 00:04:08,920
It's the Wanna One suitcase.

103
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,320
The Wanna One suitcase.

104
00:04:10,390 --> 00:04:11,590
Can you see it? Wanna One.

105
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:13,420
(Coming up shortly)

106
00:04:13,730 --> 00:04:14,730
Even your suitcase...

107
00:04:15,260 --> 00:04:16,559
That's the Wanna One suitcase.

108
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,760
Where did you get this?

109
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,600
At last, the day has come.

110
00:04:21,070 --> 00:04:22,570
I was so nervous and couldn't go to sleep.

111
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:24,800
The thought of hanging out with them made me excited.

112
00:04:25,270 --> 00:04:27,040
Being on a reality show again...

113
00:04:27,570 --> 00:04:28,570
makes me feel awkward.

114
00:04:29,470 --> 00:04:30,809
- Hello. - Okay.

115
00:04:30,810 --> 00:04:32,040
Hello.

116
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,450
It's tough, isn't it?

117
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:35,950
Salute.

118
00:04:36,910 --> 00:04:38,080
My friend.

119
00:04:38,550 --> 00:04:40,449
- Hey, you're here. - Right.

120
00:04:40,450 --> 00:04:41,790
You're not too tired from the flight?

121
00:04:41,990 --> 00:04:43,619
- He said it was fine. - He looks good.

122
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:44,689
Right. He still...

123
00:04:44,690 --> 00:04:46,260
He looks the same.

124
00:04:47,090 --> 00:04:48,329
(The emperor enters.)

125
00:04:48,330 --> 00:04:49,890
You're here.

126
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,130
(Min Hyun joins them too.)

127
00:04:52,430 --> 00:04:54,229
Jae Hwan, how's your album coming along?

128
00:04:54,230 --> 00:04:55,499
Yes. We shot the music video.

129
00:04:55,500 --> 00:04:57,069
I also filmed "Men on a Mission" by myself.

130
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:59,170
I was so nervous. We usually star on shows as a team.

131
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:01,009
- But going there alone... - Right.

132
00:05:01,010 --> 00:05:02,269
I think I saw the trailer.

133
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:04,139
You really watch everything we star on.

134
00:05:04,140 --> 00:05:05,810
The clips show up in my feed.

135
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:07,510
We're all connected too.

136
00:05:08,410 --> 00:05:10,419
- Right. - How are we connected?

137
00:05:10,420 --> 00:05:12,320
We're destiny.

138
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:15,390
(Wanna One is destiny itself.)

139
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,489
He's definitely getting carried away now.

140
00:05:19,490 --> 00:05:21,530
I love our group, Wanna One, wholeheartedly.

141
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:23,529
- So do we. That's why we're here. - Everyone...

142
00:05:23,530 --> 00:05:24,599
- We all love our group too. - We...

143
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,729
Right. We wouldn't have come if we didn't love it wholeheartedly.

144
00:05:26,730 --> 00:05:28,029
Hello.

145
00:05:28,030 --> 00:05:29,169
(King Danjong walks in.)

146
00:05:29,170 --> 00:05:30,329
Come on.

147
00:05:30,330 --> 00:05:31,639
Here comes the box-office hit actor.

148
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:34,369
(How happy we are)

149
00:05:34,370 --> 00:05:36,610
(King Danjong has come)

150
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:40,480
Your Majesty.

151
00:05:40,780 --> 00:05:42,250
I thought you would wear hanbok.

152
00:05:42,750 --> 00:05:45,149
- What? Hanbok? - Why would I wear hanbok?

153
00:05:45,150 --> 00:05:46,450
I thought you would wear hanbok.

154
00:05:47,050 --> 00:05:48,120
Why are your cheeks red?

155
00:05:48,290 --> 00:05:49,489
I'm wearing blush.

156
00:05:49,490 --> 00:05:50,490
- Cheek blush? - Really?

157
00:05:50,690 --> 00:05:52,620
You got your makeup done like an idol star after all these years.

158
00:05:53,020 --> 00:05:54,030
It's been a while.

159
00:05:54,230 --> 00:05:56,490
(The Winking Cutie is building his storyline with his gaze.)

160
00:05:56,790 --> 00:05:59,229
Didn't the movie sell over ten million tickets?

161
00:05:59,230 --> 00:06:00,870
It sold 16 million tickets.

162
00:06:01,930 --> 00:06:04,570
Is it the 2nd or 3rd highest-grossing movie of all time?

163
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:06,599
- It's now the third highest. - Really?

164
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,870
Ji Hoon, this is so cool.

165
00:06:08,140 --> 00:06:09,209
Ji Hoon.

166
00:06:09,210 --> 00:06:11,110
- I don't have a big present. - What is it?

167
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:13,810
You enhanced the position of our group, Wanna One.

168
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:15,550
(Laughing)

169
00:06:16,310 --> 00:06:18,749
What are you talking about? I didn't do anything.

170
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:20,280
- What... - I'm so grateful.

171
00:06:20,420 --> 00:06:21,420
So...

172
00:06:21,820 --> 00:06:22,920
Did you get him a present?

173
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,759
(Excited)

174
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:27,529
(Jae Hwan finally reveals what's in his suitcase.)

175
00:06:27,530 --> 00:06:28,959
- What's this? - Look what I brought.

176
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,629
Did he show you these?

177
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:31,929
What are all these?

178
00:06:31,930 --> 00:06:33,200
(Fresh cucumbers and carrots)

179
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,199
I've strictly been following my diet.

180
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,799
(Thanks to him, they get some healthy food.)

181
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,200
This is good.

182
00:06:38,770 --> 00:06:39,800
I cut them myself.

183
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:41,940
- You cut them? - Didn't your mom...

184
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:43,509
- You cut them? - Didn't your mom do it for you?

185
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:44,510
Right.

186
00:06:44,511 --> 00:06:46,410
- My mom cut them herself. - Right.

187
00:06:47,550 --> 00:06:48,709
Hello.

188
00:06:48,710 --> 00:06:50,749
- Hello. - Hey.

189
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:51,750
(Seong Wu arrives in the waiting room.)

190
00:06:52,780 --> 00:06:54,050
You're late.

191
00:06:54,450 --> 00:06:55,489
- I'm sorry. - What?

192
00:06:55,490 --> 00:06:56,590
- I'm sorry. - Why are you late?

193
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,060
Is that backpack from the military?

194
00:06:58,260 --> 00:06:59,860
No, it's from Nike.

195
00:07:00,590 --> 00:07:01,790
(Is there a problem?)

196
00:07:01,890 --> 00:07:03,160
I bought it online.

197
00:07:03,490 --> 00:07:05,830
- What's this? - Cleansing oil.

198
00:07:06,060 --> 00:07:07,199
I need to borrow it from you.

199
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,430
- You didn't bring yours? - No.

200
00:07:08,730 --> 00:07:09,999
Why do you want to use mine?

201
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,099
I didn't bring it, so I could borrow yours.

202
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:12,100
Buy your own.

203
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:13,909
Look at his facial expression.

204
00:07:13,910 --> 00:07:15,240
(Teasing Seong Wu is fun.)

205
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:18,380
- Here they go. - Here they go.

206
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:20,510
There's Dumb Seong Wu.

207
00:07:20,511 --> 00:07:23,209
- I mean, I paid money for it. - Okay.

208
00:07:23,210 --> 00:07:24,979
- I bought it with my own money. - Okay. I'll borrow from Dae Hwi.

209
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:25,980
I bought it online.

210
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:29,320
(Hurrying)

211
00:07:30,450 --> 00:07:31,460
Wait.

212
00:07:32,190 --> 00:07:33,360
You didn't get the elevator.

213
00:07:34,230 --> 00:07:35,530
It went up.

214
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:36,959
I'm late.

215
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:38,030
(The oldest member is late and worried.)

216
00:07:38,900 --> 00:07:40,230
He's here. Ji Sung.

217
00:07:40,970 --> 00:07:42,029
(The leader arrives.)

218
00:07:42,030 --> 00:07:43,030
Mr. Leader.

219
00:07:44,070 --> 00:07:45,939
- I'm sorry I'm late. - Why are you so late?

220
00:07:45,940 --> 00:07:47,239
- I'm sorry I'm late. - It's 8am.

221
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,969
Ji Sung, you look good today.

222
00:07:48,970 --> 00:07:50,739
How many treatments have you had at the dermatologist?

223
00:07:50,740 --> 00:07:52,240
Do you know how much money I spent on this face?

224
00:07:52,740 --> 00:07:53,740
- You spent a fortune, right? - Hey.

225
00:07:53,741 --> 00:07:55,550
I spent tens of thousands of dollars on this face.

226
00:07:56,050 --> 00:07:57,349
I was like Pikachu.

227
00:07:57,350 --> 00:07:59,020
(Pikachu with the million-volt charge)

228
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,549
I got so many electric shocks.

229
00:08:00,550 --> 00:08:02,650
- You look so great. - Gosh, no.

230
00:08:02,850 --> 00:08:04,690
You look so much better than before.

231
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,290
(At that moment...)

232
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,260
Oh, hey!

233
00:08:09,990 --> 00:08:11,500
- It's Sung Woon. - Oh, hey!

234
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:13,500
What's up with your shoes?

235
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,500
(Shocked)

236
00:08:15,970 --> 00:08:16,970
(What about my shoes?)

237
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,270
(Eye-catching)

238
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:21,640
They're way too bright.

239
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:23,979
Why did you wear those shoes?

240
00:08:23,980 --> 00:08:25,009
Your shoes caught my eye...

241
00:08:25,010 --> 00:08:26,039
- before your face did. - Exactly.

242
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,810
Really? I don't know. But I heard these were good shoes.

243
00:08:28,050 --> 00:08:29,079
Apparently, their price is going up.

244
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:30,619
- Really? - Yes.

245
00:08:30,620 --> 00:08:32,650
- You love making good investments. - Yes.

246
00:08:33,890 --> 00:08:35,350
So Woo Jin is the last one.

247
00:08:35,390 --> 00:08:37,720
Let's kick him out or something when he comes.

248
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:41,790
Let's tell him not to come.

249
00:08:42,930 --> 00:08:44,859
(Woo Jin, who might get kicked out, finally crawls out of the van.)

250
00:08:44,860 --> 00:08:46,230
(Glancing)

251
00:08:46,460 --> 00:08:49,900
Sung Woon is making a fuss because I'm the last one to arrive.

252
00:08:50,740 --> 00:08:51,899
He was always the last one to arrive.

253
00:08:51,900 --> 00:08:54,069
But he's so happy that he's not the last one today.

254
00:08:54,070 --> 00:08:56,110
(Super excited)

255
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,140
He's here.

256
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:02,610
- Hey! - Oh, no.

257
00:09:02,950 --> 00:09:04,519
Get your hands out of your pockets.

258
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:05,919
I guess his hands get cold easily.

259
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,080
Why do you look so arrogant?

260
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:10,149
- What's he going for? - What's going on?

261
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:11,159
What is it? Tell us.

262
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,319
Let me talk.

263
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:14,429
Why are you guys so angry this morning?

264
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:16,089
- What's wrong with your voice? - I have tonsillitis.

265
00:09:16,090 --> 00:09:17,929
- Really? - He said his throat hurt yesterday.

266
00:09:17,930 --> 00:09:20,030
Why did you get sick yesterday?

267
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:22,930
It's just my luck.

268
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,069
(Sounding utterly suspicious)

269
00:09:26,070 --> 00:09:28,009
- You're doing that on purpose. - Hey.

270
00:09:28,010 --> 00:09:29,269
- Hey. - You did that on purpose, right?

271
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:30,609
- Stop fooling around. - You're doing an impression.

272
00:09:30,610 --> 00:09:32,839
- You're doing an impression. - Don't try to sound cool.

273
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,049
Stop lying. Come on.

274
00:09:34,050 --> 00:09:35,610
Don't fake your voice now.

275
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,119
Sure, it sounds okay.

276
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:40,690
- Come on. What was that? - Seriously.

277
00:09:41,390 --> 00:09:42,819
- I'm trying to show that I'm sick. - I see.

278
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:45,560
I got worried. We need to have fun together.

279
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,230
- So everyone is here. - We're all here.

280
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:51,099
By the way, I recognise...

281
00:09:51,100 --> 00:09:52,529
- a lot of the cameramen here. - Right.

282
00:09:52,530 --> 00:09:54,400
- Right. We recognise all of them. - Yes.

283
00:09:55,770 --> 00:09:57,669
You know the staff...

284
00:09:57,670 --> 00:09:59,640
from "WANNA ONE GO: Zero Base?"

285
00:10:00,140 --> 00:10:01,140
I'd love to see them again. I'm curious.

286
00:10:01,141 --> 00:10:02,610
I don't even know how they've been.

287
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:04,510
I'd love to meet the directors.

288
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:06,439
(So the staff from previous seasons are back.)

289
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,549
They reunited for us...

290
00:10:07,550 --> 00:10:09,009
- after all these years. - This is amazing.

291
00:10:09,010 --> 00:10:10,379
- It's like we're time-travelling. - Right.

292
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:12,750
Seriously. It feels like 2017 all over again.

293
00:10:13,250 --> 00:10:15,489
Remember Sangam Day from all those years ago?

294
00:10:15,490 --> 00:10:17,589
Some of us were really popular. Remember?

295
00:10:17,590 --> 00:10:19,019
Ji Hoon, Jin Young...

296
00:10:19,020 --> 00:10:21,259
Dae Hwi's pictures looked great too.

297
00:10:21,260 --> 00:10:22,890
Only some of us were popular then.

298
00:10:23,130 --> 00:10:25,799
Seong Wu, Daniel, and I walked around together back then.

299
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,399
But no one paid us any attention. Do you remember?

300
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,870
There was only one photo of me online.

301
00:10:29,270 --> 00:10:30,300
Really?

302
00:10:31,470 --> 00:10:32,599
Seong Wu looked really cool.

303
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,740
What?

304
00:10:34,070 --> 00:10:36,210
- What's this? - Hold on.

305
00:10:36,510 --> 00:10:38,380
- What is this? - Are they school uniforms?

306
00:10:39,780 --> 00:10:41,309
I guess we're going to wear them today.

307
00:10:41,310 --> 00:10:42,310
I see!

308
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:43,709
- Let's check them out. - No?

309
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:45,620
- This is the same colour. - Really?

310
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:48,049
- Are we going to wear them today? - Should I check from the front?

311
00:10:48,050 --> 00:10:49,449
Wait, they look a bit different.

312
00:10:49,450 --> 00:10:51,889
- They sort of look like hanbok. - Right.

313
00:10:51,890 --> 00:10:53,289
The collars look special. They're not regular school uniforms.

314
00:10:53,290 --> 00:10:54,329
Right.

315
00:10:54,330 --> 00:10:56,459
- I'll go and put it on. - Sounds good.

316
00:10:56,460 --> 00:10:58,099
- Let's go together. - Wait.

317
00:10:58,100 --> 00:10:59,829
- I'm really flustered. - Okay.

318
00:10:59,830 --> 00:11:01,699
When they said we would start WANNA ONE GO: Back to Base,

319
00:11:01,700 --> 00:11:02,769
I thought we'd go back...

320
00:11:02,770 --> 00:11:04,799
to "WANNA ONE GO: Zero Base" or our debut with "Energetic."

321
00:11:04,800 --> 00:11:07,740
But we're going back to the start of our competition.

322
00:11:10,810 --> 00:11:12,579
But we're going back to the start of our competition.

323
00:11:12,580 --> 00:11:14,080
(Walking away)

324
00:11:16,410 --> 00:11:17,850
Why did he tell me that?

325
00:11:20,550 --> 00:11:22,119
- He's gotten weird. - Hurry.

326
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,120
Okay.

327
00:11:23,121 --> 00:11:24,520
(It's time to get changed.)

328
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:27,830
(Wanna One is putting on the team uniform for the opening ceremony.)

329
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:30,430
This hanbok suit looks fancy and stylish.

330
00:11:30,830 --> 00:11:32,299
Both of us have been in period pieces.

331
00:11:32,300 --> 00:11:33,929
Right. We've been in period pieces.

332
00:11:33,930 --> 00:11:36,270
- So we're used to wearing hanbok. - Right, we're used to it.

333
00:11:36,330 --> 00:11:38,099
It looks great because it looks traditional.

334
00:11:38,100 --> 00:11:39,899
Let's go. We look great. Let's do this.

335
00:11:39,900 --> 00:11:41,540
(Their hearts flutter at the thought of meeting Wannables in this.)

336
00:11:41,810 --> 00:11:42,970
Do we look good on camera?

337
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:47,339
This is the same camera angle from before.

338
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:49,910
We filmed our reality show in this camera angle.

339
00:11:51,250 --> 00:11:52,680
(Taking a selfie in the same camera angle)

340
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:54,790
One, two, three.

341
00:11:55,090 --> 00:11:56,490
- Let's go, guys. - Okay.

342
00:11:56,790 --> 00:11:58,120
Be on standby, Wanna One.

343
00:11:58,260 --> 00:11:59,460
Wannables are on standby.

344
00:11:59,690 --> 00:12:01,660
- Let's go! - Today...

345
00:12:02,330 --> 00:12:03,330
Hey, I'm nervous.

346
00:12:03,331 --> 00:12:05,059
Wait. I don't want to be in the front.

347
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:06,099
- What? - I'm nervous.

348
00:12:06,100 --> 00:12:07,529
Hey, Ji Hoon. You stand in the front.

349
00:12:07,530 --> 00:12:09,369
- No. Why me? - Hey, come here.

350
00:12:09,370 --> 00:12:10,399
- Come on. - Come here.

351
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,639
- Stop it. Don't do that. - No.

352
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:13,539
- That's a lot of pressure. - You should go in the front.

353
00:12:13,540 --> 00:12:15,109
- This is a lot of pressure. - I'll be in the front.

354
00:12:15,110 --> 00:12:16,939
- Min Hyun, you go in the front. - Okay.

355
00:12:16,940 --> 00:12:18,139
Seong Wu should join you.

356
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:19,779
Small fish like us should stand back.

357
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:21,649
No. Tall ones should go in the front.

358
00:12:21,650 --> 00:12:23,009
So the three of them are in the front.

359
00:12:23,010 --> 00:12:24,849
- What if our fans can't see us? - The rest of us are following them?

360
00:12:24,850 --> 00:12:25,879
Someone should film us too.

361
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:27,249
Is someone filming small fish like us?

362
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:28,689
- I like it here. - Ji Hoon should go in the front.

363
00:12:28,690 --> 00:12:30,219
- This is my spot. - Ji Hoon should go in the front.

364
00:12:30,220 --> 00:12:32,390
Don't make him feel uncomfortable.

365
00:12:32,890 --> 00:12:34,089
(His 1st warning)

366
00:12:34,090 --> 00:12:35,590
That was spot on.

367
00:12:36,230 --> 00:12:38,130
(But I'm so proud of Ji Hoon.)

368
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,499
Hey, you'll get motion sickness.

369
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:42,029
(Wanna One make their way down for their entrance.)

370
00:12:42,030 --> 00:12:43,200
My gosh.

371
00:12:46,170 --> 00:12:47,539
Oh, no. I'm getting nervous.

372
00:12:47,540 --> 00:12:49,540
Same here. This feels weird.

373
00:12:50,710 --> 00:12:52,209
- Ji Sung. - When we walk out,

374
00:12:52,210 --> 00:12:53,480
will we see our fans?

375
00:12:54,580 --> 00:12:55,580
By the way,

376
00:12:55,810 --> 00:12:57,920
- this feels so weird. - Right?

377
00:12:58,220 --> 00:12:59,220
This feels surreal.

378
00:12:59,221 --> 00:13:01,090
- Right. - It does feel weird.

379
00:13:01,220 --> 00:13:02,450
It's finally sinking in.

380
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:06,189
Nothing has changed from all those years ago.

381
00:13:06,190 --> 00:13:07,420
- Right. - It's the same feeling.

382
00:13:11,100 --> 00:13:12,600
I think they're calling for us.

383
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:18,739
- Did you see that? - Yes.

384
00:13:18,740 --> 00:13:19,800
- Did you see that? - Yes.

385
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,340
(The members of Wanna One come together before meeting Wannables.)

386
00:13:23,410 --> 00:13:25,039
All right. This is the hand for Daniel.

387
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:26,680
Can someone put down a hand for Kuan Lin?

388
00:13:27,010 --> 00:13:28,249
We got it. Okay. There are 11 hands.

389
00:13:28,250 --> 00:13:29,850
- One, two, three. - Two, three.

390
00:13:30,010 --> 00:13:32,650
(A star made of 11 genuine hearts)

391
00:13:32,820 --> 00:13:35,219
When our hands touched just now,

392
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:36,620
I didn't feel so nervous anymore.

393
00:13:37,290 --> 00:13:39,460
- What's up with you? - Do you have a script or something?

394
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:41,389
- Is there a teleprompter? - I didn't get anything.

395
00:13:41,390 --> 00:13:42,390
I'm serious.

396
00:13:42,391 --> 00:13:43,990
"When our hands touched just now,"

397
00:13:44,760 --> 00:13:45,859
- "I didn't feel nervous." - It was like a play.

398
00:13:45,860 --> 00:13:47,300
That's why I'm not an actor.

399
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:48,730
I only sing.

400
00:13:48,770 --> 00:13:50,299
- It's been a long time... - We can do this.

401
00:13:50,300 --> 00:13:51,599
since we gathered our fans like this.

402
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,339
- Let's make this a special day. - Down?

403
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:54,569
- Okay. Let's push our hands down. - Or up?

404
00:13:54,570 --> 00:13:55,570
- Down. - Down?

405
00:13:55,571 --> 00:13:56,839
- Up? - One, two, three.

406
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:57,979
- Let's go. - Let's go.

407
00:13:57,980 --> 00:13:59,980
(Let's do our best for Wannables who waited for a long time.)

408
00:14:01,450 --> 00:14:02,949
- Let's go! - We got this!

409
00:14:02,950 --> 00:14:04,479
- Let's have some fun. - Let's go.

410
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:06,379
- Let's go, Wanna One. - Let's have fun.

411
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:08,890
- I'm so nervous. - Here we go.

412
00:14:10,690 --> 00:14:11,819
Be on standby, Wannables.

413
00:14:11,820 --> 00:14:13,620
(Did a lot of their fans show up despite the unfavourable conditions?)

414
00:14:14,090 --> 00:14:15,330
(Amazed)

415
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:20,159
I think at least 100 fans would show up.

416
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:22,230
I'll tell my family and relatives.

417
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:27,469
(Many Wannables filled the site contrary to their worry.)

418
00:14:27,470 --> 00:14:28,669
Hello.

419
00:14:28,670 --> 00:14:31,810
(The reunion of Wanna One and Wannables)

420
00:14:32,910 --> 00:14:35,250
(A huge crowd)

421
00:14:35,780 --> 00:14:38,780
(They reunite in Sangam, the 1st place they met 9 years ago.)

422
00:14:39,780 --> 00:14:40,919
Hello.

423
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:42,550
(His eyes are fixed on Wannables.)

424
00:14:43,490 --> 00:14:44,619
Hello.

425
00:14:44,620 --> 00:14:46,790
(Only Wannables catch Wanna One's eye at this moment.)

426
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:51,059
Wannables came to see us despite the bad weather...

427
00:14:51,060 --> 00:14:52,760
when they heard Wanna One would get together.

428
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:55,870
I was so grateful. Seeing them made me very happy.

429
00:14:56,700 --> 00:14:59,940
(They're unable to look away from Wannables.)

430
00:15:00,540 --> 00:15:02,670
It was an emotional moment.

431
00:15:03,110 --> 00:15:06,209
I realised they had been waiting for us during all these years...

432
00:15:06,210 --> 00:15:07,909
and they hadn't forgotten about us yet.

433
00:15:07,910 --> 00:15:09,950
It almost made me cry.

434
00:15:10,310 --> 00:15:13,680
(When Wanna One gets together, Wannables show up.)

435
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:17,350
(Walking sideways like crabs to see Wannables)

436
00:15:20,020 --> 00:15:21,259
(They can't stop looking at Wannables.)

437
00:15:21,260 --> 00:15:24,030
(Turning his back to the camera)

438
00:15:25,030 --> 00:15:28,300
(Happy to see their fans)

439
00:15:28,670 --> 00:15:30,030
You look handsome.

440
00:15:30,230 --> 00:15:32,500
(Greeting the fans before getting up on the stage)

441
00:15:33,070 --> 00:15:36,940
(All the members are on stage now.)

442
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,779
Gosh, so many of our fans showed up.

443
00:15:38,780 --> 00:15:40,209
Hey, so many people came.

444
00:15:40,210 --> 00:15:41,680
- The crowd seems endless. - Gosh.

445
00:15:41,850 --> 00:15:42,909
I got goosebumps.

446
00:15:42,910 --> 00:15:44,319
Let's say hello. Two, three.

447
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:48,019
- All I want to do is Wanna One. - All I want to do is Wanna One.

448
00:15:48,020 --> 00:15:50,019
- Hello. We're Wanna One. - Hello. We're Wanna One.

449
00:15:50,020 --> 00:15:51,389
It's been a long time.

450
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:53,590
(It's been a long wait.)

451
00:15:53,690 --> 00:15:56,090
We missed you guys too!

452
00:15:56,930 --> 00:15:58,700
Oh, my. I'm getting goosebumps.

453
00:16:01,270 --> 00:16:06,500
(The reunion after 7 years gives them mixed feelings.)

454
00:16:08,910 --> 00:16:11,309
(Wannables have been waiting in the same spot for them...)

455
00:16:11,310 --> 00:16:13,710
(all these years with the same unwavering love.)

456
00:16:14,010 --> 00:16:15,679
Gosh, we haven't met our fans like this in a while.

457
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:18,879
(We haven't met our fans like this in a while.)

458
00:16:18,880 --> 00:16:20,349
I might tear up a bit.

459
00:16:20,350 --> 00:16:23,390
(I might tear up a bit.)

460
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:28,029
(Getting more grateful for their unchanging love)

461
00:16:28,030 --> 00:16:30,530
- So many people showed up. - I haven't felt this in a while.

462
00:16:32,730 --> 00:16:37,570
(All the longing for each other finally brings them together today.)

463
00:16:38,070 --> 00:16:39,969
To keep our promise to you,

464
00:16:39,970 --> 00:16:41,339
we, Wanna One, have come back in April...

465
00:16:41,340 --> 00:16:43,139
with the spring breeze in the air.

466
00:16:43,140 --> 00:16:45,840
(Wanna One is back!)

467
00:16:49,250 --> 00:16:51,319
This is the opening ceremony to mark the start of a new season...

468
00:16:51,320 --> 00:16:53,279
and hope for a successful one.

469
00:16:53,280 --> 00:16:55,689
I'm the MC of the opening ceremony...

470
00:16:55,690 --> 00:16:58,019
for WANNA ONE GO: Back to Base. My name is Lee Dae Hwi.

471
00:16:58,020 --> 00:16:59,089
I'm Yoon Ji Sung.

472
00:16:59,090 --> 00:17:01,559
- We're the Lovables. - We're the Lovables.

473
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:03,129
- So cute. - They're so adorable.

474
00:17:03,130 --> 00:17:04,960
- How lovable. - So cute.

475
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:07,869
WANNA ONE GO has returned after seven years.

476
00:17:07,870 --> 00:17:09,599
We have a special reason...

477
00:17:09,600 --> 00:17:11,269
behind inviting Wannables at the start of our new season.

478
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:13,799
Ji Hoon. Why don't you tell us on behalf of our group?

479
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:15,769
Ji Hoon. Why don't you tell us on behalf of our group?

480
00:17:15,770 --> 00:17:19,480
Sure. Yes. Well...

481
00:17:20,410 --> 00:17:22,350
- Hey. - Okay.

482
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:25,849
Getting off to a good start is the most important.

483
00:17:25,850 --> 00:17:26,850
So to...

484
00:17:26,851 --> 00:17:29,619
save...

485
00:17:29,620 --> 00:17:31,020
this moment...

486
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:33,460
(Wannables: We're going to pass out.)

487
00:17:33,820 --> 00:17:34,829
(Members: You have our respect.)

488
00:17:34,830 --> 00:17:37,800
We wanted to kick off our new season with Wannables.

489
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:39,960
Yes.

490
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:42,000
Min Hyun.

491
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:43,000
(Help me out!)

492
00:17:43,170 --> 00:17:45,670
Right. All of us...

493
00:17:46,700 --> 00:17:47,739
(Min Hyun helps him escape.)

494
00:17:47,740 --> 00:17:49,639
have been doing our own projects like filming dramas.

495
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:52,009
We were nervous to meet you since it had been a while.

496
00:17:52,010 --> 00:17:55,109
We had no idea that so many of you would show up.

497
00:17:55,110 --> 00:17:57,079
I'd like to thank everyone for showing up.

498
00:17:57,080 --> 00:17:58,279
- Thank you. - Thank you.

499
00:17:58,280 --> 00:17:59,849
- Thank you. - Thank you.

500
00:17:59,850 --> 00:18:01,650
(Thank you for showing up despite the bad weather.)

501
00:18:01,890 --> 00:18:04,419
Daniel and Kuan Lin look...

502
00:18:04,420 --> 00:18:05,989
super excited too.

503
00:18:05,990 --> 00:18:07,059
Is that so?

504
00:18:07,060 --> 00:18:08,889
Kuan Lin is definitely excited.

505
00:18:08,890 --> 00:18:11,629
Actually, Daniel texted us yesterday.

506
00:18:11,630 --> 00:18:14,359
He wished us a good fan meeting today.

507
00:18:14,360 --> 00:18:15,569
(Thank you, Daniel! We'll do our best...)

508
00:18:15,570 --> 00:18:16,729
(and have fun at the shoot on your behalf too.)

509
00:18:16,730 --> 00:18:17,970
(The actual chat between Daniel and Dae Hwi)

510
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:19,340
- Jae Hwan. Should we go... - Yes.

511
00:18:19,341 --> 00:18:21,339
to Daniel and interview him?

512
00:18:21,340 --> 00:18:22,540
- Should we? - Ask him how he feels.

513
00:18:23,070 --> 00:18:24,170
Daniel.

514
00:18:24,710 --> 00:18:26,009
Let me start with a salute.

515
00:18:26,010 --> 00:18:27,140
(Reporter Jae Hwan is on the move.)

516
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:29,910
How does it feel to meet Wannables?

517
00:18:30,750 --> 00:18:31,750
It feels great.

518
00:18:31,751 --> 00:18:32,879
(Daniel is also a ventriloquist?)

519
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:34,050
(Hey, this worked!)

520
00:18:34,220 --> 00:18:36,019
- I think Daniel is here! - He's here.

521
00:18:36,020 --> 00:18:37,090
- He's here. - Yes.

522
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:40,520
(Wannables in a stir)

523
